---
const manifest = await import('../../public/data/manifest.json').then(m => m.default).catch(() => ({ version: 'seed', generatedAt: 'pending', discoveredFromDataGovIe: 0 }));
const context = await import('../../public/data/context-bundle.json').then(m => m.default).catch(() => ({ datasets: [], entities: [], relationships: [] }));
const datasetCount = Number(manifest.discoveredFromDataGovIe ?? 0) + context.datasets.length;
const entities = context.entities ?? [];
const relationships = context.relationships ?? [];
---
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <title>Ireland Public Context Graph</title>
    <meta name="description" content="A hosted public-data context graph and MCP access layer for Ireland." />
    <style>
      :root{font-family:Inter,ui-sans-serif,system-ui,sans-serif;color:#102018;background:#f7faf8}body{margin:0}.wrap{max-width:1120px;margin:auto;padding:32px 20px}.hero{padding:56px 0}.badge{display:inline-block;background:#dff8e8;color:#095227;padding:6px 10px;border-radius:999px;font-weight:700;font-size:13px}.grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(230px,1fr));gap:16px}.card{background:white;border:1px solid #dfe9e2;border-radius:18px;padding:20px;box-shadow:0 4px 18px #1232}.muted{color:#52645a}.button{display:inline-block;background:#0b6b37;color:white;text-decoration:none;border-radius:12px;padding:12px 16px;font-weight:700;margin-right:8px;margin-top:8px}.button.secondary{background:#17342a}code{background:#edf4ef;padding:2px 5px;border-radius:6px}a{color:#0b6b37}footer{border-top:1px solid #dfe9e2;margin-top:48px;padding:24px 0;color:#52645a}.mono{font-family:ui-monospace,SFMono-Regular,Menlo,monospace;font-size:13px;word-break:break-all}</style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <main class="wrap">
      <section class="hero">
        <span class="badge">Data-only contextual intelligence layer</span>
        <h1>Ireland Public Context Graph</h1>
        <p class="muted">A provenance-first hub that collates, normalizes, versions and links public Irish datasets across transport, roads, planning, environment, weather, demographics, health, education, public services, infrastructure and local government.</p>
        <p><strong>The project provides data and relationships only.</strong> It does not provide conclusions, causation, safety determinations, official designations, engineering assessments, legal opinions or recommendations.</p>
        <a class="button" href="/data/context-bundle.json">Download context bundle</a>
        <a class="button secondary" href="/mcp">Hosted MCP endpoint</a>
      </section>
      <section class="grid">
        <div class="card"><h2>{datasetCount}</h2><p>Dataset records catalogued</p></div>
        <div class="card"><h2>{entities.length}</h2><p>Seed graph entities generated</p></div>
        <div class="card"><h2>{relationships.length}</h2><p>Seed relationships linked</p></div>
        <div class="card"><h2>{manifest.version}</h2><p>Current data release</p></div>
      </section>
      <section>
        <h2>Hosted MCP</h2>
        <p>Connect Claude, Codex or another remote-MCP client to the hosted endpoint once deployed:</p>
        <p class="mono">https://ireland-public-context-graph-mcp.&lt;cloudflare-subdomain&gt;.workers.dev/mcp</p>
        <p>The MCP exposes read-only data tools such as <code>list_datasets</code>, <code>get_dataset_metadata</code>, <code>search_entities</code>, <code>get_relationships</code>, <code>get_context_graph</code>, <code>get_data_coverage</code> and <code>get_export_links</code>.</p>
      </section>
      <section>
        <h2>Data artifacts</h2>
        <div class="grid">
          <a class="card" href="/data/dataset-catalog.json">Dataset catalogue</a>
          <a class="card" href="/data/entities.json">Entities</a>
          <a class="card" href="/data/relationships.json">Relationships</a>
          <a class="card" href="/data/observations.json">Observations</a>
          <a class="card" href="/data/manifest.json">Release manifest</a>
        </div>
      </section>
      <section>
        <h2>Claim boundary</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Public and derived contextual datasets only.</li>
          <li>No official findings, legal opinions, engineering assessments, causation conclusions, safety determinations or recommendations.</li>
          <li>Interpretation by users or third-party AI tools is external to this project.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>
      <footer>Generated: {manifest.generatedAt}. Source: <a href="https://github.com/the-fluid-company/ireland-public-context-graph">GitHub</a>.</footer>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>
